@startuml
title Notes on Messages

participant Client
participant Server
participant Database

Client -> Server : login(user, pass)
note right : Authentication request\nwith credentials

Server -> Database : findUser(user)
note left : Query user table

Database --> Server : userRecord
note right : Returns null if not found

Server --> Client : authToken
note left
    JWT token containing:
    - userId
    - roles
    - expiry
end note

Client -> Server : getData(token)
note right : Token in Authorization header

Server --> Client : data
note left : Paginated response

@enduml
